---
title: Beef & Pork Pasta Bolognese with Cherry Tomatoes & Pear Salad
description: Packed with the rich flavours of a classic Italian tomato sauce, you'll find it hard to believe this beef bolognese didn't involve hours of cooking. Plus, with veggies hidden in the sauce, it creates a beautifully textured and mouth-watering meal everyone will love.

*We’ve replaced the penne in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f4cbc9587dccd5cb5f1d7c-c5b305f7.jpeg
